<h2>Research</h2>

<p>
  Research is generated by <strong>Mage Towers</strong>. Each active Mage Tower produces
  <strong><%= @buildings['mage_tower']&.production&.to_f || 1 %> research point per turn</strong>
  and consumes
  <strong><%= @buildings['mage_tower']&.settings&.dig('research_gold_need') || 100 %> gold per turn</strong>.
  Set your current research focus on the Research tab in the game.
</p>

<h4>Research Cost Formula</h4>
<p>
  The cost to gain the next level increases super-linearly with your total research levels across all types:
</p>
<p><code>cost = 10 + (total_levels² × √total_levels)</code></p>
<p>Early levels are cheap; later levels become extremely expensive. Plan research priorities carefully.</p>

