<div class="alert alert-info mt-3">
  <strong>Tip:</strong> Early-game priorities: <em>Food Production</em> and <em>Wood Production</em>
  support growth. <em>Explorers</em> is excellent when exploring heavily.
  <em>Army Upkeep Cost</em> and <em>Army Training Cost</em> save significant resources as your army grows.
  Max these out (50 levels = 50% reduction) before going higher on uncapped types.
</div>
